# Homebrew (macOS/Linux)

Homebrew install vesctl on macOS or Linux:

```bash
brew tap robinmordasiewicz/tap
brew install vesctl
```

**Upgrade to latest version:**

```bash
brew upgrade vesctl
```

**Uninstall:**

```bash
brew uninstall vesctl
```

## Verify Installation

After installation, verify vesctl is working:

```bash
